            "failure_message": "Requires engaged attention with confusion present, plus an 'unlock' moment: confusion drops noticeably (crossing or drop magnitude) or agency/control jumps upward. Excludes boredom/apathy (not checked-out) and caps panic (not a threat spiral)."
